ived backups in directory'=>'Tips: Klik tombol di bawah ini untuk memindai semua cadangan yang diunggah atau diterima di direktori','This will contain all of your posts, pages, comments, terms and images (original images, featured images and thumbnails).'=>'Ini akan berisi semua artikel, halaman, komentar, istilah, dan gambar Anda (gambar asli, gambar unggulan, dan thumbnail).','This request will delete the backup being downloaded, are you sure you want to continue?'=>'Permintaan ini akan menghapus cadangan yang sedang diunduh, apakah Anda yakin ingin melanjutkan?','This request might delete the backup being downloaded, are you sure you want to continue?'=>'Permintaan ini mungkin menghapus cadangan yang sedang diunduh, apakah Anda yakin ingin melanjutkan?','This does not appear to be a WXR file, missing/invalid WXR version number'=>'Ini sepertinya bukan file WXR, nomor versi WXR hilang/tidak valid','This backup is locked, are you sure to remove it? This backup will be deleted permanently from your hosting (localhost) and remote storages.'=>'Cadangan ini terkunci, apakah Anda yakin untuk menghapusnya? Cadangan ini akan dihapus secara permanen dari hosting Anda (localhost) dan penyimpanan remote.','This backup can only be deleted manually'=>'Cadangan ini hanya dapat dihapus secara manual','There was an error when reading this WXR file'=>'Ada kesalahan saat membaca file WXR ini','There is no default remote storage configured. Please set it up first.'=>'Tidak ada penyimpanan remote default yang dikonfigurasi. Mohon atur terlebih dahulu.','There are two ways available to send us the debug information. The first one is recommended.'=>'Ada dua cara yang tersedia untuk mengirimkan informasi debug kepada kami. Yang pertama direkomendasikan.','The time-out is not your server PHP time-out. With the execution time exhausted, our plugin will shut the process of restore down. If the progress of restore encounters a time-out, that means you have a medium or large sized website, pl